{
  "id": "6a098e0af09a72a182f9052e",
  "title": "C言語の精神",
  "created": 1779011099,
  "updated": 1779011110,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a098e0af09a72a182f9052e",
      "text": "C言語の精神",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011099,
      "updated": 1779011099
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1a000000000063f098",
      "text": "Keep the spirit of C",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011099,
      "updated": 1779011104
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e22000000000063f0a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011106,
      "updated": 1779011106
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f099",
      "text": "　プログラマを信頼する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011106
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09a",
      "text": "　　Trust the programmer.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09b",
      "text": "　プログラマが行うべき必要作業を妨げない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09c",
      "text": "　　Don't prevent the programmer from doing what needs to be done.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09d",
      "text": "　小さく単純な言語仕様",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09e",
      "text": "　　Keep the language small and simple.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f09f",
      "text": "　一つの操作に一つの方法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f0a0",
      "text": "　　Provide only one way to do an opreation.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f0a1",
      "text": "　移植性が保証されなくても、早い処理速度",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f0a2",
      "text": "　　Make it fast,even if it is not guaranteed to be provide.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f0a3",
      "text": "　実証可能な安全性とセキュリティをサポートする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e1b000000000063f0a4",
      "text": "　　Make support for safety and security demonstrable.",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011100,
      "updated": 1779011100
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e25000000000063f0a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011110,
      "updated": 1779011110
    },
